'''瑞秋·艾希莉·普蕾頓'''（{{lang-en|Rachel Ashley Platten}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://repertoire.bmi.com/writer.asp?blnWriter=True&blnPublisher=True&blnArtist=True&page=1&fromrow=1&torow=25&querytype=WriterID&keyid=1013619&keyname=PLATTEN+RACHEL+ASHLEY&CAE=494825608&Affiliation=BMI|title=Songwriter/Composer: Platten Rachel Ashley|publisher=Broadcast Music, Inc.|accessdate=2015-06-07|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160202155238/http://repertoire.bmi.com/writer.asp?blnWriter=True&blnPublisher=True&blnArtist=True&page=1&fromrow=1&torow=25&querytype=WriterID&keyid=1013619&keyname=PLATTEN+RACHEL+ASHLEY&CAE=494825608&Affiliation=BMI|archivedate=2016-02-02}}</ref>，{{bd|1981年|5月20日}}）是一位美國[[流行_(音樂類型)|流行樂]]歌手及作曲家。她最著名的是她的2015年單曲〈[[戰鬥之歌|戰鬥之歌]]〉，這首單曲曾登上美國[[告示牌百強單曲榜|《告示牌》百強單曲榜]]第6名，以及《[[告示牌_(雜誌)|告示牌]]》數位單曲榜冠軍，意味著這首歌在美國2015年6月28日這週是最佳銷售單曲。另外，她也以她的2011年單曲〈1,000 Ships〉出名，這首歌曾登上美國《告示牌》{{le|40強成人音樂榜|Adult Top 40}}第24名。<ref>{{Cite web |first=Stephen |last=Bradley |date=2011-09-13 |url=http://communities.washingtontimes.com/neighborhood/riffs-music/2011/sep/13/concert-review-rachel-platten/|title=Concert review: Rachel Platten|publisher=''[[The_Washington_Times|The Washington Times]]''|accessdate=2012-02-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120411165713/http://communities.washingtontimes.com/neighborhood/riffs-music/2011/sep/13/concert-review-rachel-platten|archivedate=2012-04-11}}</ref><ref name="dailymail">{{cite news |last=Brown |first=Laurel |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3123665/Taylor-Swift-shows-midriff-racy-white-costume-brings-friend-Rachel-Platten-onstage-duet-Philadelphia-concert.html |title=Taylor Swift shows off her midriff in racy white costume as she brings friend Rachel Platten onstage for duet during Philadelphia concert |work=[[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]] |publisher=DMG Media |date=2015-06-14 |accessdate=2015-07-10 |archive-date=2020-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804005007/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3123665/Taylor-Swift-shows-midriff-racy-white-costume-brings-friend-Rachel-Platten-onstage-duet-Philadelphia-concert.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==早年生活==
普蕾頓生於1981年5月20日，帕梅拉（Pamela）與保羅·普蕾頓（Paul Platten）之女。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Platten|first1=Rachel|title=Happy Birthday to my absolutely incredible mom!|url=https://www.facebook.com/rachelplattenmusic/photos/a.405296569785.181405.6346584785/10151220563194786/?_rdr=p&source=46&type=1|website=facebook|accessdate=2015-06-22|date=2013-01-10}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=SUMNER M. PLATTEN Obituary|url=http://www.legacy.com/obituaries/bostonglobe/obituary.aspx?pid=160499318|website=The Boston Globe|accessdate=2015-06-22|date=2012-10-18|archive-date=2019-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190301074503/http://www.legacy.com/obituaries/bostonglobe/obituary.aspx?pid=160499318|dead-url=no}}</ref>她在[[美國|美國]][[牛頓_(麻薩諸塞州)|牛頓]]{{le|牛頓中心 (麻薩諸塞州)|Newton Centre, Massachusetts|牛頓中心}}長大，從5歲開始學習古典鋼琴，之後在高中時彈奏吉他。她在高中時進入{{le|白金漢布朗和尼古拉斯學校|Buckingham Browne & Nichols}}就讀，並加入了該校的歌唱團體。<ref>{{cite news |last=McFeeters |first=Stephanie |url=https://www.bostonglobe.com/lifestyle/names/2015/06/16/newton-centre-native-rachel-platten-talks-about-performing-onstage-with-taylor-swift/u9WaKEPbezD6Q241l32mzI/story.html |title=Rachel Platten on performing with Taylor Swift |work=bostonglobe.com |publisher=The Boston Globe |date=2015-06-16 |accessdate=2015-07-10 |archive-date=2020-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130143050/https://www.bostonglobe.com/lifestyle/names/2015/06/16/newton-centre-native-rachel-platten-talks-about-performing-onstage-with-taylor-swift/u9WaKEPbezD6Q241l32mzI/story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>普蕾頓之後在2003年從[[康乃狄克州|康乃狄克州]]的[[三一學院_(康乃狄克州)|三一學院]]畢業，取得國際關係學位。<ref>{{cite news |last=Elise |first=Kei-Rahn |url=https://commons.trincoll.edu/tripod/2014/11/12/trinity-alumna-rachel-platten-performs-at-the-mill/ |title=Trinity alumna Rachel Platten performs at The Mill |work=The Trinity Tripod |publisher=Trinity College |date=2014-11-12 |accessdate=2015-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017234325/http://commons.trincoll.edu/tripod/2014/11/12/trinity-alumna-rachel-platten-performs-at-the-mill/ |archive-date=2015-10-17 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>她在19歲時參加了海外學習計畫，前往[[千里達島|-{zh-cn:特立尼达岛;zh-hk:千里達島;zh-tw:千里達島;}-]]的一間外交官辦事處與一間唱片公司作實習。在此期間，她在2002年支援朋友的樂團，在{{le|國際索卡君主|International Soca Monarch}}音樂大賽的決賽於80,000名觀眾面前演唱。根據普蕾頓表示，從此刻起她決定全心專注在音樂上面。<ref name="idolator1">{{cite web|last1=Wass|first1=Mike|title=Rachel Platten Talks "Fight Song," Making A Difference And Her Long Road To The Top: Idolator Interview|url=http://www.idolator.com/7589634/rachel-platten-interview-fight-song-debut-ep-video|website=Idolator|accessdate=2015-06-22|date=2015-04-20|archive-date=2021-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210418173058/https://www.idolator.com/7589634/rachel-platten-interview-fight-song-debut-ep-video|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="teenvogue">{{cite news |last=Firman |first=Tehrene |url=http://www.teenvogue.com/story/rachel-platten-interview |title=There's a Solid Chance You've Already Heard (and Loved) Rachel Platten's Music—Here's Why |work=Teen Vogue |publisher=[[Condé_Nast|Condé Nast]] |date=2015-05-28 |accessdate=2015-07-10 |archive-date=2020-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030190750/https://www.teenvogue.com/story/rachel-platten-interview |dead-url=no }}</ref>之後，她便搬到[[紐約市|紐約市]]的[[格林尼治村|格林尼治村]]，開始在一支翻唱樂團中演奏。剛開始她與一位鼓手在村莊巡迴演出，最終開始在全國巡迴。<ref name="teenvogue"/><ref name="USA TODAY">{{cite news |last=Mansfield |first=Brian |url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/music/ontheverge/2015/04/26/rachel-platten-fight-song-on-the-verge/25991723/ |title=On the Verge: Rachel Platten's ready to fight |work=USA TODAY |publisher=Gannett Company |date=2015-04-26 |accessdate=2015-07-10 |archive-date=2020-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200313210623/https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/music/ontheverge/2015/04/26/rachel-platten-fight-song-on-the-verge/25991723/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>她也曾與許多的慈善機構合作，像是「隨叫隨到音樂家計劃」（Musicians on Call）、<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.musiciansoncall.org/site/News2?page=NewsArticle&id=5370 |title=MOC Congratulates MOC Volunteer Rachel Platten |work=Musicians On Call |accessdate=2015-07-10 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305104004/http://www.musiciansoncall.org/site/News2?page=NewsArticle&id=5370 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.musiciansoncall.org/site/News2?page=NewsArticle&id=5343 |title=2011-03-15 New York Volunteer Musician, Rachel Platten, Shares Inspiring Experience |work=Musicians On Call |accessdate=2015-07-10 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305134810/http://www.musiciansoncall.org/site/News2?page=NewsArticle&id=5343 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>[[瑞安·西克雷斯特|瑞安·西克雷斯特]]基金會，<ref>{{cite news |url=http://ryanseacrestfoundation.org/2015/06/02/rachel-platten-sings-fight-song-at-seacrest-studios-in-orange-county/ |title=Rachel Platten Sings 'Fight Song' at Seacrest Studios in Orange County |work=ryanseacrestfoundation.org |publisher=Ryan Seacrest Foundation |date=2015-06-02 |accessdate=2015-07-10 |archive-date=2018-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180329222918/http://ryanseacrestfoundation.org/2015/06/02/rachel-platten-sings-fight-song-at-seacrest-studios-in-orange-county/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>以及擔任「Music Unites」的大使。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.musicunites.org/blog-all/music-unites-emerson-brings-mu-womens-empowerment-ambassador-rachel-and-singer-bess-rogers-to-emerson-college/ |title=MUSIC UNITES EMERSON BRINGS MU WOMEN’S EMPOWERMENT AMBASSADOR RACHEL AND SINGER BESS ROGERS TO EMERSON COLLEGE |work=musicunites.org |publisher=Music Unites |date=2011-03-11 |accessdate=2015-07-10 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304103200/http://www.musicunites.org/blog-all/music-unites-emerson-brings-mu-womens-empowerment-ambassador-rachel-and-singer-bess-rogers-to-emerson-college/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==職業生涯==

===2003－14年：《Trust in Me》與《Be Here》===
普蕾頓在2003年發行了她的首張錄音室專輯《Trust in Me》。<ref>{{cite web|title=Trust In Me|url=http://www.mtv.com/music/artist/platten__rachel/albums.jhtml?albumId=929890|publisher=MTV|accessdate=2012-07-30}}</ref>他的第二張專輯《Be Here》由{{le|Rock Ridge Music|Rock Ridge Music}}唱片公司在2011年推出，<ref>{{cite web|url= http://allmusic.com/album/be-here-r2154168/review|title= All Music Guide Review of Be Here by William Ruhlmann|work=[[AllMusic|AllMusic]]|accessdate=2015-07-10}}</ref>她曾稱這是一張樣本歌曲的合輯。<ref name="USA TODAY"/>而她在2007年推出的歌曲〈Seven Weeks〉曾出現在電影《{{le|尋找完美情人|The Good Guy (film)}}》當中。<ref name="examiner">{{cite news |url=http://www.examiner.com/article/rachel-platten-and-caitlin-rose-fresh-female-singer-songwriters-on-the-rise |title=Rachel Platten and Caitlin Rose - fresh female singer-songwriters on the rise |work=Examiner.com |publisher=AXS Digital Group |date=2012-03-08 |accessdate=2015-07-10 |archive-date=2016-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160706033315/http://www.examiner.com/article/rachel-platten-and-caitlin-rose-fresh-female-singer-songwriters-on-the-rise |dead-url=no }}</ref>她也為[[ABC家庭|ABC家庭]]的電視劇《{{le|珍，愛時尚|Jane by Design}}》創作[[主題曲|主題曲]]〈Work of Art〉。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1743904/|title=Jane by Design|work=imdb.com|publisher=[[IMDb|IMDb]]|accessdate=2015-07-10|archive-date=2021-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421072038/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1743904/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="examiner"/>她的歌曲〈Begin Again〉也在ABC家族的電視劇《[[美少女的謊言|美少女的謊言]]》第100集〈Miss Me x100〉中被使用。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt3691228/soundtrack|title="Pretty Little Liars" Miss Me x100 (TV Episode 2014) - Soundtracks - IMDb|work=imdb.com|publisher=[[IMDb|IMDb]]|accessdate=2015-07-10|archive-date=2021-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210220014344/https://www.imdb.com/title/tt3691228/soundtrack|dead-url=no}}</ref>另外，還有在[[VH1|VH1]]的《{{le|籃球明星的妻子：洛杉磯版|Basketball Wives LA}}》中的〈Don't Care What Time It Is〉一曲，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vh1.com/shows/music/basketball-wives-la-2/season-2-episode-3-songs/ |title=Basketball Wives LA 2 Season 2 Episode 3 Songs |work=vh1.com |publisher=[[VH1|VH1]] |date=2012-09-24 |accessdate=2015-07-10 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304075526/http://www.vh1.com/shows/music/basketball-wives-la-2/season-2-episode-3-songs/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>以及[[MTV|MTV]]的《{{le|尋找卡特|Finding Carter}}》中的〈You're Safe〉皆是普蕾頓的創作。<ref>{{cite news |last=Greenaway |first=Johnathan |url=http://soundtrack.mtv.com/post/music-from-finding-carter-season-1-ep-8/ |title=Music from Finding Carter: Season 1, Ep. 8 |work=soundtrack.mtv.com |publisher=[[MTV|MTV]] |date=2014-08-19 |accessdate=2015-07-10 |archive-date=2015-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151121023940/http://soundtrack.mtv.com/post/music-from-finding-carter-season-1-ep-8/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2014年6月27日，普蕾頓首度在{{le|We Heart It|We Heart It}}上發布〈戰鬥之歌〉。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Platten|first1=Rachel|title=I am so excited to debut #FightSong with @weheartit !!!|url=https://twitter.com/RachelPlatten/status/482541614234345472|website=Twitter|publisher=Rachel Platten|date=2014-06-27|accessdate=2015-07-10|archive-date=2021-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207050522/https://twitter.com/RachelPlatten/status/482541614234345472|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===2015年至今===
普蕾頓於2015年4月加盟[[哥倫比亞唱片|哥倫比亞唱片]]，並且發行了〈[[戰鬥之歌_(瑞秋·普蕾頓歌曲)|戰鬥之歌]]〉單曲。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.columbiarecords.com/news/825 |title=BREAKOUT SINGER/SONGWRITER RACHEL PLATTEN JOINS COLBIE CAILLAT AND CHRISTINA PERRI ON TOUR THIS SUMMER |work=[[Columbia_Records|Columbia Records]] |publisher=[[Sony_Music_Entertainment|Sony Music Entertainment]] |date=2015-04-08 |accessdate=2015-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150711085223/http://www.columbiarecords.com/news/825 |archive-date=2015-07-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>之後在5月發行的《戰鬥之歌》迷你專輯，<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.columbiarecords.com/news/834 |title=RACHEL PLATTEN RELEASES FIGHT SONG EP TODAY |work=[[Columbia_Records|Columbia Records]] |publisher=[[Sony_Music_Entertainment|Sony Music Entertainment]] |date=2015-04-08 |accessdate=2015-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150711085225/http://www.columbiarecords.com/news/834 |archive-date=2015-07-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>更登上[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|《公告牌》二百强专辑榜]]第26名。<ref name="Billboard"/>這首歌也曾被用在《[[美少女的謊言|美少女的謊言]]》第五季的聖誕節特集，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt3981672/soundtrack|title="Pretty Little Liars" How the 'A' Stole Christmas (TV Episode 2014) - Soundtracks - IMDb|work=imdb.com|publisher=[[IMDb|IMDb]]|accessdate=2015-07-10|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305231535/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt3981672/soundtrack|dead-url=no}}</ref>以及[[澳洲|澳洲]][[七號電視網|七號電視網]]電視劇《[[復仇_(電視劇)|復仇]]》的預告當中。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QF4Hbt-hh6k|title=Revenge 4x06 Australian Promo - Seven Network 2015|website=[[YouTube|YouTube]]|publisher=AUtvPROMOS|accessdate=2015-07-10|archive-date=2020-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201012141359/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QF4Hbt-hh6k|dead-url=no}}</ref>同樣也出現在[[CBS_(電視網)|CBS]]於2015年5月上映的電視劇《[[女超人_(美國電視劇)|女超人]]》預告，<ref name="dailymail"/>以及[[福特汽車|福特汽車]]的電視廣告當中。<ref>{{cite web|title=Paced by Rachel Platten Hit 'Fight Song,' New Ford Edge Ad Campaign Seeks to Connect with Unstoppable People|url=https://media.ford.com/content/fordmedia/fna/us/en/news/2015/05/29/rachel-platten-ford-edge-ad-campaign.html|website=Ford.com|accessdate=2015-06-22|date=2015-05-29|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304193643/https://media.ford.com/content/fordmedia/fna/us/en/news/2015/05/29/rachel-platten-ford-edge-ad-campaign.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

普蕾頓在2015年{{le|艾力克斯與席耶拉|Alex & Sierra}}和{{le|安迪·格拉默|Andy Grammer}}聯合巡迴演唱會《The Good Guys & A Girl Tour》中擔任嘉賓。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Boedeker|first1=Hal|title=Alex & Sierra joining Andy Grammer on tour|url=http://www.orlandosentinel.com/entertainment/tv/tv-guy/os-alex-sierra-andy-grammer-tour-20150221-post.html|website=Orlando Sentinel|accessdate=2015-02-21|date=2015-06-23|archive-date=2019-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190220180120/https://www.orlandosentinel.com/entertainment/tv/tv-guy/os-alex-sierra-andy-grammer-tour-20150221-post.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>她也在6月13日於[[泰勒絲|泰勒絲]]的《[[1989巡迴演唱會|1989巡迴演唱會]]》中演唱〈戰鬥之歌〉，之後將在[[蔻比·凱蕾|蔻比·凱蕾]]與[[克瑞斯蒂娜·佩瑞|克瑞斯蒂娜·佩瑞]]的《The Girls Night Out, Boys Can Come Too Tour》擔任開場嘉賓。<ref>{{cite news |last=Lipshutz |first=Jason |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6598088/taylor-swift-bring-out-rachel-platten-for-fight-song-in-philly |title=Watch Taylor Swift Bring Out Rachel Platten for 'Fight Song' in Philadelphia |work=billboard.com |publisher=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]] |date=2015-06-14 |accessdate=2015-07-10 |archive-date=2020-09-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922083707/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6598088/taylor-swift-bring-out-rachel-platten-for-fight-song-in-philly |dead-url=no }}</ref>

